{"about_the_game":"<br><br>Phylakterion is a co-op psychological horror game, playable for 1-4 people. You and your team enter haunted places to find a possessed item \u2013 make sure to stay alert, because the entity possessing it does not take your presence kindly and will try to stop you!<br>Use different tools to locate the possessed item and find out what kind of entity is possessing it \u2013 Can you see the item\u2019s reflection in a mirror? Does it scream when you drop it? Does the entity write with the blood of its victims? Then use the right rituals to destroy the vessel before the entity finds you! Can you retain your sanity and finish the task at hand?<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>3-step exorcism</strong>: Search, identify, destroy!<br></li><li> <strong>Companions</strong>: Companions help your investigation! Choose from dogs, cats, or birds, each affecting your play style!<br></li><li> <strong>Talent System</strong>: Earn talent points to customize your characters the way you want to!<br></li><li> <strong>7 different tools</strong>: You\u2019ll need ghost hunting equipment, like Geiger-counters, cameras, or notebooks, to locate the vessel, identify the ghost possessing it, and destroy it!<br></li><li> <strong>1-4 players</strong>: Play alone or with your friends.<br></li><li> <strong>Afterlife</strong>: You might die if you\u2019re not careful, but you can still be helpful to your team!</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2201070?t=1698765826","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201070/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1698765826","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1698765826","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1698765826","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"des